    <!-- Instant example -->
    <string name="instant_description">With Nutrient Instant (Document Engine), it’s easier than ever to add real-time collaboration features to your Nutrient-powered app, allowing your users to seamlessly share, edit and annotate PDF documents across iOS, Android and Web apps.\n\nThe Nutrient SDKs for Android, iOS and Web support Instant out of the box. Just connect your app to an Instant (Document Engine) server and document management and syncing is taken care of.\n\nYou can try this right here, by getting a new copy of the document or copying the URL for an existing document from nutrient.io/demo</string>

